window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The fate of our world rests in their hands.</p> <p>Hades, god-king of the Underworld, has uncovered the mastermind behind the uprising destined to set his realm and the mortal world on a collision course. But his enemy has gone to ground and finding them is proving impossible, and the longer they elude his grasp, the stronger the darkness within him grows, slowly stealing control.</p> <p>Persephone, god-queen of the Underworld, can only watch as a storm gathers on the horizon—a deadly war that threatens to strip her beloved family from her. As Hades fights his own battles against their enemy, she fights to keep the darkness within him at bay, never more aware of the danger he would be if she failed to keep it tamed.</p> <p>But when their enemy strikes out at them from the shadows, dealing a blow that changes the course of the war and incites Hades’s wrath, the leash on the monster within him snaps and he is plunged into the darkness.</p> <p>And saving this world might no longer be an option.</p> <p><i>Hades is the epic conclusion to the Guardians of Hades Romance series. This paranormal romance features the Greek god of the Underworld who is as dark as his realm, his queen of the Underworld Persephone, an enemy determined to win this war, and a cast of sizzling Greek god brothers determined to put a stop to them to protect the Underworld and our world, plus lots of action and adventure--and steamy scenes! All Guardians of Hades books have no cliffhangers, a guaranteed happily ever after, and some strong language. Enjoy!</i></p> <p><b>Grab your copy today and step into an action-packed paranormal romance world filled with mythology and mystery from </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> best-selling paranormal romance author Felicity Heaton.</b></p>"; 
